text: UHSN (Hangul/Chosongul: 유학소녀; Hanja: 留學少女) was a Korean reality show produced by Mnet. 10 international female K-pop fans were invited to Korea to learn about Korean popular music, culture, cuisine and history for 3 weeks. In conjunction with the 7th episode, a single titled "Popsicle" was released on July 4.
